legal representation to those who claim to have been injured physically or psychologically as a result of the negligence or wrongdoing of another person company government agency or other entity personal injury lawyers tend to practice primarily the area of law known as tort law even though personal injury lawyers are trained and licensed to practice virtually any field of law they generally only handle cases that fall under tort law including work injuries automobile and other accidents defective products medical mistakes and slip and fall accidents more links accident lawyers in arizona attorneys in arizona consumer protection lawyers in arizona malpractice  negligence lawyers in arizona personal injury lawyers in arizona product liability lawyers in arizona fry john j attorney attorneys  corporate business lawyers curley robert a attorney attorneys bryant christopher attorney attorneys hicks leon attorney at law attorneys hays keith j attorney construction lawyers  consumer protection lawyers  product liability lawyers foxworth billy f attorney at law adoption lawyers  attorneys  criminal defense lawyers  family lawyers brown edward d attorney asset protection lawyers  attorneys  corporate business lawyers  corporate finance  securities lawyers  estate planning  administration lawyers arkell j david attorney arbitration  mediation services  arbitration  mediation services attorneys  attorneys  construction lawyers  trial lawyers galvas walter w attorney attorneys  real estate attorneys nylander nick attorney attorneys  criminal defense lawyers  personal injury lawyers bledsoe stephen m attorney attorneys  corporate business lawyers  employment  labor lawyers  franchise  licensing lawyers  trial lawyers maddox james m attorney attorneys jewel bryan a attorney attorneys baker paul k attorney accident lawyers  attorneys  medical malpractice lawyers winston  maher appeals lawyers ritter kim l attorney attorneys  employment  labor lawyers  insurance lawyers hardy asht