ranted disciplineclarke’s troubles were the result of his failure to keep proper records of his trust account as a result he overpaid fees to himself underpaid four clients and bounced checks he also used the account to pay personal and office expenses while waiting for settlement funds to come inin mitigation he has no record of discipline he immediately made restitution and no clients were harmed he has taken steps to improve his accounting procedures start new search » robert f clarke  miami fl  intelius sign in we found robert f clarke in miami fl robert f clarke intelius found that robert f clarke is a male between  and  years old from miami fl we have connected them to  addresses  phones and  relatives or associates get report now age robert f clarke is in his s robert has lived in miami fl washington dc hampton va roberts relatives haydee clarke elsa clarke emily clarke valerie clarke robert f clarke zodiac signgemini gendermale professional status chairman at zoning get report now want to know more about robert get a comprehensive background report find full phone numbers and other contact information when available all from billions of available public records continue below for more details about robert or use our people search engine to find others get background check on robert f clarke get a criminal check on robert f clarke get a public record report on robert f clarke get a people search report on robert f clarke robert f clarkes contact information known cities lived in find out where robert f clarke has lived as well as robert f clarkes phone numbers and email addresses robert f clarke has lived in  states florida address for robert f clarke  s  t miami fl has lived in miami fl washington dc get full address report phone numbers associated with robert f clarke    miami fl    miami fl   get full phone report email addresses associated with robert f clarke get email report robert f clarkes professional information information regarding robert f clarke